'''Janis''' is a woman on the plane who offered up EDs to help [[Lance]].

==History==
Janis was on a flight out of Seattle when they encountered severe turbulence, injuring several other passengers. Later, when [[Lance]] struggled to breathe due to pulmonary hypertension, Nathan asked [[Dave]] to ask around for EDs to help open up the vessels around his lungs. Janis overheard that and offered up her husband's medicine to give to Lance.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
She is married. Her husband uses EDs.
